components.cell.typeChecker

Class DoubleTypeChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • components.cell.typeChecker.DoubleTypeChecker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypeChecker2

    public class DoubleTypeChecker
extends java.lang.Object
implements TypeChecker2
    The DoubleTypeChecker class implements the TypeChecker2 interface to handle checking and parsing of objects as Double types.

    This class provides methods to check if an object can be parsed as a Double, to get the corresponding CellType, and to parse the object into a Double. 

     
 DoubleTypeChecker doubleChecker = new DoubleTypeChecker();
 boolean isDouble = doubleChecker.check("123.45");
 CellType cellType = doubleChecker.getCellType();
 Object parsedValue = doubleChecker.parse("123.45");
